###  https://w3id.org/nmdc/sfas-brcs/sfa_type
nmdc_sfas_brcs:sfa_type rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                        rdfs:range nmdc_sfas_brcs:SFAType .


###  https://w3id.org/nmdc/sfas-brcs/technologies_developed
nmdc_sfas_brcs:technologies_developed rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
