###  https://w3id.org/nmdc/sfas-brcs/brave_sorghum_anthracnose
nmdc_sfas_brcs:brave_sorghum_anthracnose rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                  nmdc_sfas_brcs:OtherProgram ;
                                         schema1:alternateName "SABI" ;
                                         schema1:description "BRaVE project investigating molecular interactions between sorghum (a bioenergy crop), its anthracnose-disease causative fungal pathogen Colletotrichum sublineola (Cs), and antifungal biocontrol bacteria to create disease-resilient bioenergy crops. Uses computational and experimental approaches to study plant-pathosystem interactions." ;
