                                           nmdc_sfas_brcs:ScientificFocusArea ;
                                  schema1:description """The Watershed Function SFA develops predictive understanding of how mountainous watersheds retain and release water, nutrients, carbon, and metals. Research focuses on interacting impacts of warming and drought on hydro-biogeochemical functioning.
